      "text": "# Key Components:\n\nChatService - Manages conversations & messages\nInvestmentAgent - Streaming agent with tool use\nScratchpad - Context window management (100k tokens)\nToolExecutor - Executes tools (market data, search)\nLiteLLM - Multi-provider LLM routing",
